<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="yard-n">yard <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /jɑːd/    美 /jɑːrd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>院子；庭院：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a farm yard 
农家院</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a yard sale 
(在自家院子进行的)旧货出售</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We cleaned up the yard and painted the house. 
我们打扫了院子，粉刷了房子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-0914">2.★ <strong>[长度单位，=0.914米] 码</strong></h4></div>